Value RULE_NAME (\S+)
Value POLICY (\S+)
Value SESSION (\S+)
Value SOURCE_ZONE (\S+)
Value DESTINATION_ZONE (\S+)
Value ACTION (\S+)

Start
  ^\srule name -> Continue.Record
  ^\s*rule name ${RULE_NAME}
  ^\s*policy ${POLICY}
  ^\s*session ${SESSION}
  ^\s*source-zone ${SOURCE_ZONE}
  ^\s*destination-zone ${DESTINATION_ZONE}
  ^\s*action ${ACTION}